message: "They don't have to worry about whether he is going to believe them or not. They can tell him how they feel, and they don't have to worry that they'll be blamed, or that somebody is going to tell them that they've done something wrong."

data.description: A 3-year-old Labrador and Bernese Mountain Dog mix is helping child survivors of sex trafficking find the calm to talk about their trauma.
data.title: 'Iggy's there just for them': Therapy dog helps child sex trafficking survivors testify
